## Part 8: Typography System

```typescript
fontFamily: {
  headline: ['Cormorant', 'Georgia', 'serif'],
  body: ['DM Sans', 'system-ui', 'sans-serif'],
  serif: ['Cormorant', 'Georgia', 'serif'],
  sans: ['DM Sans', 'system-ui', 'sans-serif'],
}

// NEVER USE: Space Grotesk, Inter, Roboto, Arial, Playfair Display, Work Sans (old stack)
```

**Typography Scale:**
```
- Display:     clamp(48px, 9vw, 84px)  — Hero headlines only
- Headline:    clamp(40px, 6vw, 64px)  — Section titles
- Headline-md: clamp(36px, 5vw, 56px)  — Subsection titles
- Headline-sm: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px)  — Card titles
- Subhead:     clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 32px) — Lead paragraphs
- Body-lg:     20px                     — Emphasis body
- Body:        18px                     — Standard body
- Body-sm:     16px                     — Small text
- Eyebrow:     11px (uppercase, 2px letter-spacing)
```

