## Part 9: Spacing System (12px Base Unit)

```typescript
spacing: {
  '15': '60px',    // 12 × 5
  '18': '72px',    // 12 × 6
  '20': '80px',    // Standard section gap
  '24': '96px',    // 12 × 8
  '30': '120px',   // Blueprint outer margins (desktop)
  '40': '160px',   // Section spacing medium
  '60': '240px',   // Section padding desktop
}
```

**Section Spacing Rules:**
```css
/* Mobile */
.section { padding: 80px 24px; }

/* Tablet */
@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .section { padding: 120px 48px; }
}

/* Desktop */
@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .section { padding: 160px 96px; }
}
```

