## Part 12: Data Management Rules

### Single Source of Truth
```
✅ /schedules page is THE source for all programs, pricing, schedules
✅ Data lives in /data/*.json files
✅ Program pages redirect to /schedules (no duplicate content)
✅ Form submissions (optional): lib/leads-store writes to Supabase leads table when env is set
❌ NEVER hardcode prices in components
❌ NEVER duplicate data across pages
```

### Dates/Schedules
```
✅ Dates can appear on schedule page, cards, and modules
✅ Use consistent date formatting: "January 6, 2026"
✅ Store in data/winter2026.json, data/fall2025.json
```

