## Part 16: Testing Checklist (Every PR)

```markdown
## Performance
- [ ] Lighthouse ≥90 (Performance, Accessibility, Best Practices, SEO)
- [ ] LCP < 2.5s on 3G throttled
- [ ] CLS < 0.1
- [ ] No horizontal scroll at any breakpoint

## Accessibility
- [ ] 7:1 contrast ratio verified (WebAIM); footer/dark sections use text-white/50+ on deep-water
- [ ] Hero CTAs on dark: solid background (e.g. bg-white) for contrast
- [ ] Keyboard navigation complete
- [ ] Screen reader tested (VoiceOver/NVDA)
- [ ] Focus states visible
- [ ] Touch targets ≥48px on mobile

## Responsive
- [ ] Tested at 320px, 375px, 768px, 1024px, 1440px
- [ ] Images lazy-loaded below fold
- [ ] Text readable without zoom

## Brand
- [ ] Copy matches founder voice (calm, confident)
- [ ] No forbidden words/phrases
- [ ] Colors within palette (black/white primary)
- [ ] Typography hierarchy correct
- [ ] No duplicate data across pages
```

